00:40:38,218 --> 00:40:38,518
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah, I mean,

361
00:40:40,395 --> 00:40:41,215
[SPEAKER_03]: Councilors have any thoughts?

362
00:40:41,235 --> 00:40:45,177
[SPEAKER_03]: I mean, my thought would be, I would be curious to get the legal review and see what that says.

363
00:40:45,378 --> 00:40:47,138
[SPEAKER_03]: I would feel fine voting this out tonight.

364
