366
00:41:01,946 --> 00:41:08,770
[SPEAKER_05]: Right, and I mean, if I may, the two, basically, right now there's three sections.

367
00:41:08,890 --> 00:41:09,390
[SPEAKER_05]: One is saying,

368
00:41:10,345 --> 00:41:13,266
[SPEAKER_05]: You can't turn your lot into a trash yard.

369
00:41:14,246 --> 00:41:19,328
[SPEAKER_05]: The second one said, you can't throw trash on streets and sidewalks or parks.

370
00:41:19,928 --> 00:41:23,230
[SPEAKER_05]: And the third one says, don't put your coal out on the street.

371
00:41:23,730 --> 00:41:28,431
[SPEAKER_05]: You know, so some, I think that's where some of this is coming from, right?

372
00:41:28,471 --> 00:41:29,892
[SPEAKER_05]: We had a really fun, uh,

373
00:41:30,472 --> 00:41:42,037
